Package: mdthemes
Title: Markdown Themes for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Neitmann", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "th.neitmann@gmail.com")
Description: A collection of 'ggplot2' themes that render text as markdown/HTML. This enables
    the creation of complex formatted plot labels, e.g. titles with indiviudal words highlighted
    in different colors.
Depends:
     R (>= 3.2)
Imports:
    cowplot,
    hrbrthemes,
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0),
    ggtext,
    ggthemes,
    tvthemes
Suggests:
    glue
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
